Package: twoCoprimary
Type: Package
Title: Sample Size and Power Calculation for Two Co-Primary Endpoints
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Gosuke",
                  family = "Homma",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "my.name.is.gosuke@gmail.com",
                  comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: Provides functions to calculate sample size and power for clinical 
    trials with two co-primary endpoints. Supports both continuous endpoints 
    (Sozu et al. 2011 <doi:10.1080/10543406.2011.551329>) and binary endpoints 
    using approximate methods (Sozu et al. 2010 <doi:10.1002/sim.3972>) and 
    exact methods (Homma and Yoshida 2025 <doi:10.1177/09622802251368697>). 
    Implements linear extrapolation approach (Hamasaki et al. 2013 
    <doi:10.1002/pst.1545>) for iterative sample size determination.
